- Usually 'main' is called app.js or server.js or index.js
- If you want to add a dependecy and you want to automatically change package.json you have to write: npm install --save <dependecy>
- If you want to add a dependecy globally write: sudo npm install -g <dependecy>
- nodemon is super usefull. It allow you to not restart the server every time somethings in js file is changed 
